HEADWORD: Valvelet
<hw>Valve"let</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A little valve; a
valvule; especially, one of the pieces which compose the outer covering
of a pericarp.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

